&lt;p data-start=&quot;6014&quot; data-end=&quot;6283&quot;&gt;• Active DoD Top Secret / SCI clearance required.&lt;br data-start=&quot;6063&quot; data-end=&quot;6066&quot;&gt;• Bachelor’s degree in Business, Acquisition, or related field.&lt;br data-start=&quot;6129&quot; data-end=&quot;6132&quot;&gt;• Relevant experience based on level.&lt;br data-start=&quot;6169&quot; data-end=&quot;6172&quot;&gt;• Knowledge of federal acquisition regulations and processes.&lt;br data-start=&quot;6233&quot; data-end=&quot;6236&quot;&gt;• Strong analytical and communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
