&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the design of scalable and secure cloud infrastructures tailored to specific MC&amp;amp;FP needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full lifecycle of cloud environments, from deployment to maintenance and scaling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure alignment of cloud strategies with overall IT security and operational policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor cloud environments to optimize performance and cost-efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the Cloud Architect and Infrastructure Lead as the expert consultant on all cloud-related initiatives within the agency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cloud Strategy Development:&amp;nbsp;Creating comprehensive cloud strategies that include public, private, and hybrid cloud models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System Design and Architecture:&amp;nbsp;Designing scalable and secure cloud infrastructure that meets government security standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Service Management:&amp;nbsp;Overseeing the deployment, maintenance, and scaling of cloud services.&lt;/li&gt;
